<h2 style="color:DodgerBlue;">The Sun</h2>
 <iframe src="https://giphy.com/embed/l378xGKOFPkHM2Vxe" width="440" height="450" frameBorder="0" class="giphy-embed" allowFullScreen></iframe><p><a href="https://giphy.com/gifs/nasa-space-nasagif-l378xGKOFPkHM2Vxe">via GIPHY</a></p>
  
  <p style="color:DodgerBlue;">In the center of the solar system is a star,The Sun is a yellow dwarf star,<br>
    a hot ball of glowing gases at the heart of our solar system. Its gravity holds<br> 
    everything from the biggest planets to tiny debris in its orbit.</p>
